				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I don't understand the issue. Just wait for VBL, delay 29800 clocks, then read VBL flag. If set, NTSC, otherwise you're on PAL. If the wait VBL takes a couple of frames due to the pathological behavior, that won't mess up the check.
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; lda $2007 ; clear VBL flag<br />wvbl:&nbsp; &nbsp;lda $2007<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bpl wvbl<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ldx #52&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;; 29799 delay<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ldy #24<br />dly:&nbsp; &nbsp; dex<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bne dly<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; dey<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bne dly<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; lda $2007<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; sta ntsc_if_neg</div></div>

